M6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9maWxlcy9saXRpZ2F0aW9uL2NvbXBsYWludHMvMjAyNC9jb21wMjYwM=
zEucGRm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb217d0ae" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">its complaint</a>, which=
 is fantastic. The background:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=
On March 15, 2023, CNBC reported that Virgin Orbit was furloughing nearly a=
ll its employees and pausing operations for one week as it looked for a fun=
ding lifeline. Later that day, Virgin Orbit filed a Form 8-K with the SEC, =
disclosing that it would immediately initiate a company-wide operational pa=
use to conserve capital, pursue additional funding, and explore strategic o=
pportunities.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After markets opened the next=
 day, on March 16, 2023, Virgin Orbit=E2=80=99s stock price fell from $1.01=
 per share to $0.71 per share.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"=
>And then Brown came in. By LinkedIn:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16=
px 0;">On March 19, 2023, Brown sent an unsolicited message via LinkedIn to=
 Virgin Orbit=E2=80=99s CEO to discuss a possible =E2=80=9Ccapital injectio=
n.=E2=80=9D After the CEO responded, Brown wrote back on March 19, 2023: =
=E2=80=9CI have invested over $750mm of my personal capital, largely in thi=
s [space] vertical, and largely in stealth mode=E2=80=A6. I have the bandwi=
dth to write the $200mm.=E2=80=9D He further emphasized: =E2=80=9CI want to=
 reiterate this [sic] my capital not=E2=80=A6anyone else=E2=80=99s.=E2=80=
=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link=
.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35781629.259288/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZ=
XJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDYtMDMvZ2FtZXN0b3AtY29tZXMtcm9hcmlu=
Zy1iYWNrP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA2MjAyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3N=
