</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A dumb simple model of artificial inte=
lligence companies is:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-le=
ft: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">It would be=
 good to develop good AI (AI that helps humans), but bad to develop bad AI =
(AI that kills or enslaves humans).</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;=
">If you try to build good AI, there is some risk of building bad AI instea=
d (your robot tricks you into thinking that it=E2=80=99s nice, then enslave=
s you), so you have to be very very careful. You can=E2=80=99t move too fas=
t; you have to check carefully, at each step, to make sure that your robot =
is not secretly evil.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Company A is=
 formed by idealistic AI researchers who want to create good AI. They work =
together well for a while.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Disagre=
ements develop. Some researchers at Company A say =E2=80=9Cwe need to work =
faster to build good AI, because if we don=E2=80=99t, someone else will com=
