</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in =E2=80=9Cnonbanks do stuf=
f banks used to do,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/35781629.259288/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL2Jhbmt=
